  "text": "Direct stimulation of DCs by LPS was also tested in vitro. DCs were cultured using previously published methods. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Briefly, DCs were isolated from C57BL/6J mouse bone marrow and cultured for 10 days using RPMI 1640 medium (Thermo Fisher Scientific). On day 10, cells were left untreated or treated with 1 lL of 1 lg/lL LPS dissolved in endotoxin-free water. After 4 hours, DC cultures were collected for PCR analysis.",
